snippet.title: Ultimate Admiral: Dreadnoughts Trailer
snippet.description:
This game is the revolution in ship design and combat!

Design warships, command fleets, win the naval arms race for your nation.
Experience realistic naval fleet combat of the early 20th century.

Pre-order and play now! https://www.ultimateadmiral.com
